240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭問到，反送中期間「黑暴橫行」，對鄭國漢而言是否很大挑戰。鄭笑著稱嶺南大學的好處，是「我個地方冇戰略價值」，故未有吸引人前來「佔據校園、控制某啲路」，認為理工大學和中文大學之所以「發生咁多事」，是因為其地理位置「有戰略價值」。惟他指，校內由美心代理經營的飯堂亦曾遭破壞，有多名黑衣人於凌晨時份到飯堂打爆玻璃，批評當時社會「無法無天」。"},{"pid":"db63deda34a8eb04191c2028cc85411641862a5c","tid":2517642,"uid":301666,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"保護手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190727/s00001/f894eb92ef21e7c308c04b1f6e7e41df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190727%2Fs00001%2Ff894eb92ef21e7c308c04b1f6e7e41df.jpg&h=cad4ab43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://video-static.hk01.com/fe9e4351-6447-46d8-977c-e49a3b2f42ed_20190727_113158\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo-static.hk01.com%2Ffe9e4351-6447-46d8-977c-e49a3b2f42ed_20190727_113158&h=fd15b6e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3947cb996e92e61048390f60af3580355a7acdfc","tid":2517642,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b42acff6455e4add64dc6c066870b6c558f5f0","tid":2517642,"uid":255637,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"800d15cd96c9aca060a699ccf0b306756a6a9ec0","tid":2517642,"uid":14422,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"教育界當然委員全部外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭國漢<br />\n國籍 美國<br />\n<br />\n段崇智<br />\n國籍 美國<br />\n<br />\n史維<br />\n國籍 美國<br />\n<br />\n張翔<br />\n國籍 美國<br />\n<br />\n郭位<br />\n國籍 美國<br />\n<br />\n張仁良<br />\n國籍 美法國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國人聯盟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0